headline: Keybanc Maintains Overweight on Mid-America Apartment, Lowers Price Target to $155
summary: Keybanc  analyst Austin Wurschmidt   maintains Mid-America Apartment (NYSE:MAA) with a Overweight and lowers the price target from $170 to $155.
